<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ByeBites - AuroZeon</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #121212;
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        header .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff9800;
        }

        header nav a {
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        header nav a:hover {
            color: #ff9800;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #ff9800;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .byebites-content {
            background: #1e1e1e;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .byebites-content h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ff9800;
        }

        .byebites-content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .legal-links {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .legal-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            background: #292929;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .legal-links a:hover {
            background: #ff9800;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .app-download-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .app-store-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .app-store-buttons a {
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .app-store-buttons a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .app-store-buttons img {
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
        }

        footer p a {
            color: #ff9800;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">AuroZeon</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="byebites.html" class="active">ByeBites</a>
            <a href="byebites-privacy-policy.html">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="byebites-user-agreement.html">User Agreement</a>
            <a href="byebites-health-disclaimer.html">Health Disclaimer</a>
            <a href="byebites-support.html">Contact Us</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>ByeBites</h1>
        
        <div class="byebites-content">
            <h2>About ByeBites</h2>
            <p>ByeBites is a revolutionary solution designed to help you track and manage your food consumption habits. Our platform provides personalized insights and recommendations to improve your dietary choices and overall health.</p>
            
            <div class="app-download-section">
                <h2>Download Our App</h2>
                <p>Get started with ByeBites today! Download our app from your preferred app store.</p>
                <div class="app-store-buttons">
                    <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.byebites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <img src="https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/static/images/badges/en_badge_web_generic.png" alt="Get it on Google Play">
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/byebites/id6744876719" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        <img src="https://developer.apple.com/app-store/marketing/guidelines/images/badge-download-on-the-app-store.svg" alt="Download on the App Store">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h2>Legal Documents</h2>
            <p>Please review the following important legal documents related to ByeBites:</p>
            
            <div class="legal-links">
                <a href="byebites-privacy-policy.html">Privacy Policy - How we handle and protect your data</a>
                <a href="byebites-user-agreement.html">User Agreement - Terms and conditions for using ByeBites</a>
                <a href="byebites-health-disclaimer.html">Health Disclaimer - Important health-related information</a>
                <a href="byebites-support.html">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 AuroZeon. All rights reserved. <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>